    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your sword &amp; spade and embark on an infinite sandbox online RPG adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314350/extras/66daec7111c36da28e6ba7dc30f92da2.poster.avif?t=1731672956\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314350/extras/66daec7111c36da28e6ba7dc30f92da2.webm?t=1731672956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314350/extras/66daec7111c36da28e6ba7dc30f92da2.mp4?t=1731672956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everforge: Craft Legends presents you with an ever-expanding voxel block based procedural universe of player-created worlds to adventure in. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314350/extras/d2ec42b108882b8ea5ea49346e6ae08f.poster.avif?t=1731672956\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314350/extras/d2ec42b108882b8ea5ea49346e6ae08f.webm?t=1731672956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314350/extras/d2ec42b108882b8ea5ea49346e6ae08f.mp4?t=1731672956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own base, embark on quests, dig down to unearth treasures and rare materials to create new items with, trade with villagers and wandering merchants, cast magic spells, hunt wild animals and slay vicious monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit other player's worlds, show off your creations to other visiting players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314350/extras/0bf30225f395e87df5203a8385ed3e77.poster.avif?t=1731672956\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314350/extras/0bf30225f395e87df5203a8385ed3e77.webm?t=1731672956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314350/extras/0bf30225f395e87df5203a8385ed3e77.mp4?t=1731672956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Train skills such as Woodcutting, Mining, Blacksmithing, Crafting, and more! Increasing your skills gives bonuses when crafting, building, and digging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with other players on the skill leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your own legends, forge your destiny and head out on a journey with no end.</p>",
